The [[Thermonuclear smoke devil]]'s most profitable drops are the [[occult necklace]] ({{Coins|floor({{GEP|Occult necklace}})}}), [[smoke battlestaff]] ({{Coins|floor({{GEP|Smoke battlestaff}})}}), and the [[dragon chainbody]] ({{Coins|floor({{GEP|Dragon chainbody}})}}).

The average kill is worth {{Coins|floor({{#var:thermyAverage}})}}, taking supplies into consideration, the average kill is worth {{Coins|floor({{#var:thermyAverage}} - {{#var:suppliesPerKill}})}}.

Killing this boss requires the player to be on a slayer task. Players seeking consistent profit often prefer to kill other bosses such as [[Money making guide/Killing Zulrah|Zulrah]] or [[Money making guide/Killing Vorkath|Vorkath]].

